{"tid":2282804,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"市民朗豪坊築燈鏈紀念","createTime":"2020-11-12T06:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T06:10:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"49b560d6776febaa79cae2cd83b7dcb25f4c1a56","tid":2282804,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T06:10:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201112/5ZVH62W55NG5VDAQSOFNAYRHME/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201112%2F5ZVH62W55NG5VDAQSOFNAYRHME%2F&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2Au2WzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=9e4e4b29\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201112%2F5ZVH62W55NG5VDAQSOFNAYRHME%2F&h=bcd7bdbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201112/5ZVH62W55NG5VDAQSOFNAYRHME/</a><br />\n<br />\n市民朗豪坊築燈鏈紀念<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/C75zvimXF4U2cajFOmL6Fh9pTMo=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FJGXVF7DCNGOVLFZ2UW7OD5HQ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FC75zvimXF4U2cajFOmL6Fh9pTMo%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFJGXVF7DCNGOVLFZ2UW7OD5HQ4.jpg&h=7b1cb0c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有市民在旺角朗豪坊外舉起手機燈光，紀念中大保衞戰一周年。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年11.11多區「黎明行動」，並發生「中大保衞戰」。有網民昨晚發起「築燈鏈．照中大」行動紀念事件。晚上7時45分有逾20人在旺角朗豪坊門外舉起手機燈光連成一線，高唱《願榮光歸香港》，高叫「民族自強、香港獨立」等口號。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警到場驅趕<br />\n<br />\n約十名軍裝警員到場警告眾人違反限聚令，要求在場人士離開，警方又截查現場黑衣人士。去年被拘留在內地的王婆婆近9時到場，一人手持「Fight for Freedom」燈箱及「#save12HKYouths 」紙牌。<br />\n<br />\n大批傳媒拍攝王婆婆，近10名警員趕至，並以橙帶圍住王婆婆一人，指她有機會破壞社會安寧，涉公眾行為不檢，四分鐘內密集式發出三次警告。王婆婆反駁只是一人示威舉牌。<br />\n<br />\n其間一名警員突指「我警車都叫埋㗎喇」，在場人士即時起哄，有在場人士質問是否要拘捕王婆婆，另一警員回應稱「唔好喺度講埋啲煽動性嘅語言，呢度邊個講話要拘捕人」。警車其後到場，王婆婆即坐在地上一度堅拒離開，在場介入的「女長毛」雷玉蓮最終扶走王婆婆，警方未有帶王上警車。<br />\n<br />\n沙田新城市廣場外百步梯晚上亦有逾十人到場亮燈，王婆婆亦一度到場，有人播放純音樂版的《願榮光歸香港》支持抗爭不滅。"},{"pid":"01dcd712935bf4c7746020b90da9b4fa19243ede","tid":2282804,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T06:10:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}